{"tid":599889,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"普巴:願意和尼馬一起踢球 他代表快樂足球","createTime":"2018-03-21T00:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T01:58:07.000Z","uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cca7a2d1b145428c05447bea6f6ce3371cb3627a","tid":599889,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T00:28:57.000Z","msg":"曼聯球星普巴近日接受TyC Sports的採訪時談到了尼馬。普巴表示自己非常欣賞尼馬的風格和能力，他表示如果有朝一日兩人能夠合作，那會非常令人開心。<br />\n<br />\n　　普巴說：「是的，我喜歡尼馬，他是球場上快樂的代言人。在巴西，足球就是一切，是生命。每個人都踢球。我喜歡看到尼馬在場上比賽，展示他的技術和能力，這是一種不同的風格。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「無論在世界的任何地方，當你說出尼馬，每個人都知道他是誰。如果有一天我能和他一起踢球，這會是一件非常讓人開心的事情。」<br />\n<br />\n　　普巴今季在曼聯處境不佳，他的表現遭到了不少批評。不過如今回到國家隊，普巴看起來狀態倒是好了不少。<br />\n<br />\n　　（雷利）"},{"pid":"0094756e2ef3657a74970798fec11974a9955f98","tid":599889,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T00:32:18.000Z","msg":"不是巴西人=往死裏打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78b5c6bc52bafce730ec9f5514ca3c5b39712da","tid":599889,"uid":37735,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T00:36:58.000Z","msg":"佢2條友的性格<br />\n<br />\n應該會開拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7368dbfd07e39540c3d8c880e15e1fc4d1179906","tid":599889,"uid":6783,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"e78b5c6bc52bafce730ec9f5514ca3c5b39712da","tid":599889,"uid":37735,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T00:36:58.000Z","msg":"佢2條友的性格<br />\n<br />\n應該會開拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T00:39:48.000Z","msg":"On9 約埋一齊剪頭髮啊"},{"pid":"727d3a4c099008c4b41b2c52fc376b6627d78776","tid":599889,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7368dbfd07e39540c3d8c880e15e1fc4d1179906","tid":599889,"uid":6783,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"e78b5c6bc52bafce730ec9f5514ca3c5b39712da","tid":599889,"uid":37735,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"cited